guest_message: Hey there! I'd love to place an order with you. Can I start with a Spaghetti Carbonara? And could you add shrimp as a protein add-on? I hear it's amazing! üçùüòÑ

Hey, thanks for suggesting that! Yeah, let's go ahead and add the extra parmesan and the garlic bread to the Spaghetti Carbonara for sure. Could you also tell me a bit more about any salad options you have, maybe a Caesar Salad if possible? And the name for the order is Miguel Rodriguez.

Absolutely! I'll take a Caesar Salad with a salmon add-on, and please make it without croutons. Also, I'd love to add a Chocolate Lava Cake with strawberry ice cream on the side, and if possible, an extra scoop of ice cream. That should complete my order!
Great! Everything looks perfect with the order. I'll be there to pick it up in about 20 minutes. Thanks a lot!
